{"tid":25763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國外交部希望 美國不讓蔡英文下月外訪時在美過境","createTime":"2016-12-06T10:17:21.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T01:00:30.000Z","uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f677aa06c133a42b25e38447298a80eecddffafa","tid":25763,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:17:21.000Z","msg":"大陸外交部希望 美國不讓蔡英文在美過境 <br />\n<br />\n 2016-12-06 17:02<br />\n聯合報 記者田思怡╱即時報導 <br />\n<br />\n路透報導，大陸外交部 6日表示，蔡英文下月訪問 瓜地馬拉時，希望美國不讓蔡英文在美國過境。 大陸外交部在對路透發表的聲明中表示，大陸希望 美國「不讓蔡英文過境，不要對『台獨勢力』發出 任何錯誤訊息。」<br />\n<a href=\"http://udn.com/news/story/1/2151941\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F1%2F2151941&d=UpCGnSyyXP1JUvkUpR2X9WN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=b389feb4\" target=\"_blank\">http://udn.com/news/story/1/2151941</a>"},{"pid":"0be2d398a5c0a4d84411bd4ffdcd1934f5447403","tid":25763,"uid":47451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808c0611cc8f0ad6fa0fad0c940d56c26c77b841","tid":25763,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:19:46.000Z","msg":"睇奧巴馬軟弱到咩程度？"},{"pid":"24ec40a006fc7011da78cb1a93cfc69bd16c2600","tid":25763,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:23:12.000Z","msg":"干涉美國內政"},{"pid":"a1b4ce7c02baef3e67f38ec634cd7d980738efa0","tid":25763,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:26:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇奧巴馬軟弱到咩程度？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你阻Trump<br />\n以Trump性格 到佢上任果陣高規格接待<br />\n打多支那兩巴"},{"pid":"3e0ce6d893781da12e4ad7cf71dd0a3a260dca32","tid":25763,"uid":35410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:28:15.000Z","msg":"屌，真喺好撚煩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d586a728481509978